summary: I saw your trans! Peter fanfic ideas and all I gotta say is why are you going to transwash him?
question: I saw your trans! Peter fanfic ideas and all I gotta say is why are you going to transwash him?
answer:
T…. Transwash?

Okay, mate, you see, I am a trans man. This is a harmless au/headcanon that literal tens of thousands of trans people indulge in because positive representation is key to having good self esteem and not hating yourself.

If you happen to be a poc or LGBT, you would understand this and understand what representation means to us. But from your response, I’m unsure.

We don’t get superheros that look like us. We don’t even get mainstream characters that look like us.

We’re just having fun by making do with what we got.

Hey everyone :DJAM HERE!
A gift for a classmate and also because this movie is great! It’s just amazing in general I loved the...
body:
Hey everyone :DJAM HERE!

A gift for a classmate and also because this movie is great! It’s just amazing in general I loved the music (heck I’m not much into rapping but this movie gave me some good soundtrack), and the animation is outstanding (as an artist it’s like a gift nicely wrapped in comic book themed paper which I find comic book styles fun and unique here)

I’ve been wanting to draw something from this movie now I have an excuse to draw Miles 😂

Watch the movie it’s amazing

Art by me

God bless you :3
